00:27:48,588 --> 00:27:49,963
Ayo!

368
00:27:50,047 --> 00:27:52,172
Jangan ada yang bergerak!

369
00:27:59,630 --> 00:28:01,463
Konvoi asli dalam perjalanan.

370
00:28:12,005 --> 00:28:13,588
Jaraknya delapan kilometer.

371
00:28:16,755 --> 00:28:18,588
Itu hanya butuh enam menit.

372
00:28:18,672 --> 00:28:20,755
Waktu mereka hanya enam menit
