390
00:29:20,005 --> 00:29:21,380
Tampak mustahil, tapi...

391
00:29:22,547 --> 00:29:24,088
Palermo, jelaskan.

392
00:29:24,505 --> 00:29:27,713
Hadirin, selamat datang di Bank Spanyol.

393
00:29:28,172 --> 00:29:31,380
Kita turun 10 meter di bawah lantai,
20 meter...

394
00:29:31,713 --> 00:29:32,547
Tiga puluh meter.

395
00:29:33,255 --> 00:29:34,088
Lalu 40 meter.

396
00:29:34,547 --> 00:29:35,755
Ini dia.

397
00:29:37,588 --> 00:29:39,130
Brankas.

