Tunjukkan hormat.

405
00:29:55,838 --> 00:29:56,755
Itu pujian.

406
00:29:56,838 --> 00:29:59,547
Itu hebat. Sebuah mahakarya.

407
00:29:59,630 --> 00:30:00,630
Unik di dunia.

408
00:30:00,713 --> 00:30:04,213
Mereka menyalurkan dua sungai
